Package com.example.lotterysystemproject.Models

Class Entrant

java.lang.Object
com.example.lotterysystemproject.Models.Entrant
public class Entrant extends Object
Represents an entrant in an event lottery. This class stores information about a user who has entered a lottery for an event, including their personal details and their status in the lottery.
